"payment_terms>`: To specify when the customer has to pay the invoice."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Data de vencimento` ou :doc:`condições de pagamento "
"<customer_invoices/payment_terms>`: Para especificar quando o cliente deve "
"pagar a fatura."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/accounting/customer_invoices.rst:46
