#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:116
msgid ""
"France's `electronic invoicing reform <https://www.impots.gouv.fr/"
"professionnel/je-passe-la-facturation-electronique>`_ *(reforme de la "
"facturation électronique)* impacts all VAT-registered French companies, and "
"is being rolled out in two phases:"
msgstr ""
"A `reforma de faturamento eletrônico<https://www.impots.gouv.fr/"
"professionnel/je-passe-la-facturation-electronique>`_ da França *(reforme de "
"la facturation électronique)* impacta todas as empresas francesas "
"registradas para IVA e está sendo implementada em duas fases:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:121
msgid "From **September 1, 2026**:"
msgstr "A partir de **1º de setembro de 2026**:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:123
msgid ""
"every company must be able to receive domestic B2B e-invoices via "
"*plateformes agréées* (approved platforms) :ref:`(e-invoicing) "
"<localizations/france/e-invoicing-fac-elec-einvoicing>`"
msgstr ""
"todas as empresas devem ser capazes de receber faturas eletrônicas B2B "
"domésticas por meio de *plateformes agréées* (plataformas aprovadas) :ref:`"
"(faturamento eletrônico) <localizations/france/e-invoicing-fac-elec-"
"einvoicing>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:125
msgid ""
"large enterprises (GE) and mid-sized enterprises (ETI) must send domestic "
"B2B e-invoices :ref:`(e-invoicing) <localizations/france/e-invoicing-fac-"
"elec-einvoicing>` and must submit data to the tax authorities about certain "
"operations, such as B2C and cross-border B2B operations :ref:`(e-reporting) "
"<localizations/france/e-invoicing-fac-elec-reporting>`"
msgstr ""
"grandes empresas (GE) e empresas de médio porte (ETI) devem enviar faturas "
"eletrônicas B2B domésticas :ref:`(faturamento eletrônico) <localizations/"
"france/e-invoicing-fac-elec-einvoicing>` e devem enviar dados às autoridades "
"fiscais sobre determinadas operações, como operações B2C e B2B "
"transfronteiriças :ref:`(relatório eletrônico) <localizations/france/e-"
"invoicing-fac-elec-reporting>`"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:130
msgid ""
"From **September 1, 2027**, every company, including small and medium-sized "
"enterprises (PME) and micro-enterprises are subject to the same :ref:`e-"
"invoicing <localizations/france/e-invoicing-fac-elec-einvoicing>` "
"and :ref:`e-reporting <localizations/france/e-invoicing-fac-elec-reporting>` "
"requirements."
msgstr ""
"A partir de **1º de setembro de 2027**, todas as empresas, incluindo "
"pequenas e médias empresas (PME) e microempresas, estarão sujeitas aos "
"mesmos requisitos de :ref:`faturamento eletrônico <localizations/france/e-"
"invoicing-fac-elec-einvoicing>` e :ref:`relatório eletrônico <localizations/"
"france/e-invoicing-fac-elec-reporting>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:135
msgid ""
"Odoo is officially certified as a *plateforme agréée* (approved platform) on "
"the e-invoicing network. It supports the receipt of documents in various "
"formats (Facture-X, UBL, and CII) and the sending of documents exclusively "
"in UBL format."
msgstr ""
"O Odoo é oficialmente certificado como uma *plateforme agréée* (plataforma "
"aprovada) na rede de faturamento eletrônico. Ele suporta o recebimento de "
"documentos em vários formatos (Facture-X, UBL e CII) e o envio de documentos "
"exclusivamente no formato UBL."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:140
msgid "VAT-exempt transactions under Articles 261-261E are excluded."
msgstr ""
"Transações isentas de IVA nos termos dos Artigos 261-261E estão excluídas."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:147
msgid ""
"To activate the e-invoicing and e-reporting features, follow these "
"configuration steps:"
msgstr ""
"Para ativar os recursos de faturamento eletrônico e relatório eletrônico, "
"siga estas etapas de configuração:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:149
msgid ""
"Make sure the :guilabel:`France - E-Invoicing (Approved Platform)` "
"(`l10n_fr_pdp`) module is :doc:`installed </applications/general/"
"apps_modules>`."
msgstr ""
"Certifique-se de que o módulo :guilabel:`France - E-Invoicing (Approved "
"Platform)` (`l10n_fr_pdp`) esteja :doc:`instalado </applications/general/"
"apps_modules>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:151
msgid ""
"In the **Accounting** or **Invoicing** app, go "
"to :menuselection:`Configuration --> Settings`, scroll down to "
"the :guilabel:`French Electronic Invoicing` section, and "
"click :guilabel:`Activate Electronic Invoicing`."
msgstr ""
"No aplicativo **Financeiro** ou **Faturamento**, vá para "
":menuselection:`Configuração --> Configurações`, role até a seção "
":guilabel:`French Electronic Invoicing` e clique em :guilabel:`Activate "
"Electronic Invoicing`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:154
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Send via French electronic invoicing` window, fill in "
"the :guilabel:`Email` field with the email address of a legal representative "
"and click :guilabel:`Authenticate`:"
msgstr ""
"Na janela :guilabel:`Send via French electronic invoicing`, preencha o campo "
":guilabel:`Email` com o endereço de e-mail de um representante legal e "
"clique em :guilabel:`Authenticate`:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:157
msgid "In the pop-up window, click :guilabel:`Begin authentication`."
msgstr "Na janela pop-up, clique em :guilabel:`Begin authentication`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:158
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Accessing the legal representatives of your company` "
"window, click :guilabel:`Check status`, then select your name in "
"the :guilabel:`Please select who you are` list, and :guilabel:`Confirm`."
msgstr ""
"Na janela :guilabel:`Accessing the legal representatives of your company`, "
"clique em :guilabel:`Check status`, selecione seu nome na lista "
":guilabel:`Please select who you are` e :guilabel:`Confirm`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:161
msgid ""
"To verify your identity, click :icon:`oi-launch` :guilabel:`Open "
"authentication page`."
msgstr ""
"Para verificar sua identidade, clique em :icon:`oi-launch` :guilabel:`Open "
"authentication page`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:162
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Authentication` window, click :guilabel:`Receive a code`, "
"then enter the 5-digit code received by email and :guilabel:`Confirm`."
msgstr ""
"Na janela :guilabel:`Authentication`, clique em :guilabel:`Receive a code`, "
"insira o código de 5 dígitos recebido por e-mail e :guilabel:`Confirm`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:164
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Identity verification` window, click :guilabel:`Next`."
msgstr ""
"Na janela :guilabel:`Identity verification`, clique em :guilabel:`Next`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:165
msgid ""
"To complete verification, click the :icon:`fa-plus` :guilabel:`(plus)` icon "
"under :guilabel:`Add your document here` to upload a copy of your ID card, "
"passport, or residence permit, then click :guilabel:`Next`."
msgstr ""
"Para concluir a verificação, clique no ícone :icon:`fa-plus` :guilabel:`"
"(mais)` em :guilabel:`Add your document here` para fazer upload de uma cópia "
"do seu documento de identidade, passaporte ou autorização de residência e "
"clique em :guilabel:`Next`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:168
msgid ""
"To electronically sign the :guilabel:`Attestation de désignation de "
"plateforme agréée` (certificate of designation of an approved platform), "
"click :guilabel:`Next` to review it, then click :guilabel:`Next` again and "
"enable both options:"
msgstr ""
"Para assinar eletronicamente a :guilabel:`Attestation de désignation de "
"plateforme agréée` (certificação de designação de uma plataforma aprovada), "
"clique em :guilabel:`Next` para revisá-la, depois clique em :guilabel:`Next` "
"novamente e ative ambas as opções:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:172
msgid ":guilabel:`I acknowledge having read all the documents`."
msgstr ":guilabel:`I acknowledge having read all the documents`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:173
msgid ""
":guilabel:`I accept the general conditions of use of VIALNIK 360 and the "
"signature certificate`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`I accept the general conditions of use of VIALNIK 360 and the "
"signature certificate`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:176
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Sign`."
msgstr "Clique em :guilabel:`Sign`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:177
msgid ""
"Once the signature is confirmed, the signed attestation and terms and "
"conditions can be downloaded, if needed."
msgstr ""
"Assim que a assinatura for confirmada, o atestado assinado e os termos e "
"condições podem ser baixados, se necessário."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:180
msgid "Authentication is then successful, and the page can be closed."
msgstr "A autenticação é bem-sucedida e a página pode ser fechada."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:182
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Send via French electronic invoicing` window, "
"click :guilabel:`Refresh`."
msgstr ""
"Na janela :guilabel:`Enviar via faturamento eletrônico francês`, clique em "
":guilabel:`Atualizar`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:183
msgid ""
"Verify that the :guilabel:`Identifier` field is filled in with "
"your :abbr:`SIREN (Système d'identification du répertoire des entreprises, "
"Business Directory Identification System)` number, enable "
"the :guilabel:`Pilot Phase` option if you are configuring electronic "
"invoicing before September 1, 2026, and click :guilabel:`Validate "
"Registration`."
msgstr ""
"Verifique se o campo :guilabel:`Identificador` está preenchido com seu "
"número :abbr:`SIREN (Système d'identification du répertoire des entreprises, "
"Sistema de Identificação do Diretório de Empresas)`, ative a opção "
":guilabel:`Fase Piloto` se você estiver configurando o faturamento "
"eletrônico antes de 1º de setembro de 2026 e clique em :guilabel:`Validar "
"Registro`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:187
msgid ""
"Your French e-invoicing ID is now ready to send and receive e-invoices and "
"credit notes. Enable the following options, as needed:"
msgstr ""
"Seu ID de faturamento eletrônico francês está pronto para enviar e receber "
"faturas eletrônicas e notas de crédito. Ative as seguintes opções, conforme "
"necessário:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/france.rst:190
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Incoming Invoices Journal`: Automatically set, update if "
"necessary."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Diário de Faturas Recebidas`: Definido automaticamente, atualize "
