#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/guatemala.rst:111
msgid ""
"To locate the :guilabel:`Establishment Code` in your `SAT account <https://"
"portal.sat.gob.gt/>`_, go to :menuselection:`FEL --> Administración de "
"Establecimientos`. The list of registered establishments is displayed along "
"with their corresponding codes."
msgstr ""
"Para localizar o :guilabel:`Código do Estabelecimento` na sua `conta SAT "
"<https://portal.sat.gob.gt/>`_, vá para :menuselection:`FEL --> "
