#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1516
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Tariff Fraction` and :guilabel:`UMT Aduana` must be set, similar "
"to the :ref:`external trade <l10n/mx/external-trade>` flow."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Fração Tarifária` e :guilabel:`UMT Aduana` devem ser definidos, "
"semelhante ao fluxo de :ref:`comércio exterior <l10n/mx/external-trade>`."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1518
msgid ":guilabel:`Material Type` must be set."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Tipo de Material` deve ser definido."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/mexico.rst:1520
msgid ""
"Then, when creating a :guilabel:`Delivery Guide` from a delivery or receipt, "
