"dependendo do usuário selecionado ao gerar as credenciais da API |GRE| no "
"portal do |SUNAT|."

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:799
msgid "Operator"
msgstr "Operador"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/peru.rst:801
