msgstr "FACe"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:342
#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:388
msgid ""
"Make sure the :guilabel:`Spain - Facturae EDI` (`l10n_es_edi_facturae`) "
