#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:348
msgid "To configure FACe, follow these steps:"
msgstr "Para configurar o FACe, siga estas etapas:"

#: ../../content/applications/finance/fiscal_localizations/spain.rst:350
msgid ""
"Go to :menuselection:`Accounting --> Configuration` "
"or :menuselection:`Invoicing --> Configuration`, and "
"select :guilabel:`Certificates` in the :guilabel:`Spain Facturae EDI` "
