"Verify the default package is in use by navigating "
"to :menuselection:`Accounting App --> Settings` and under "
"the :guilabel:`Fiscal Localization` section at the top, look for the "
"`Generic Chart Template` selection to be listed next to "
"the :guilabel:`Package` field label. This chart template includes the "
"necessary settings for the US localization for the Odoo *Accounting* app."
msgstr ""
